  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Notes: "This class uses MouseInput direction player -> mouse world pos to move
    the local position of a gameobject that's used as a look at target by the hands
    \bpositioned in the weapon handguard.\nThis values are hardcoded in the public
    variables, feel free to mess around with them to get a feeling of what each of
    them do. To reset the values simply right click on top of the script name and
    hit Reset."
