  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  notes: This class uses MouseInput direction player -> mouse world pos and other
    variables like rate, min offset angle and max offset angle to determine an offset
    angle that will be added to the shoulder as an extra rotation. This is an important
    part of the behaviour that controls the rotation of the shoulders, with the correct
    values both shoulders match their rotation in relation to the weapon that's being
    held by the character.
  rate: 60
  minOffsetAngle: 0
  maxOffsetAngle: 50
  shoulderMain: {fileID: 5496811085240251864}
  isUpdateCalledLocally: 0
